text=!!! Arduino%0a* Banzi, M, '''Getting started with Arduino''', O’Reilly, 2009%0a* Tom Igoe, '''Making Things Talk: Using Sensors, Networks, and Arduino to see, hear, and feel your world''' Published September 2011, O'Reilly%0a* Greg Borenstein, '''Making Things See: 3D vision with Kinect, Processing, Arduino, and MakerBot''',Published February 2012, O'Reilly%0a* Karvinen, K, '''Make Arduino bots and gadgets''', 2011, O’Reilly %0a* Morrison, R, '''Practical electronics : a self-teaching guide'''%0a* Torrente, O,'''Arduino.Curso práctico de formación''', RC libros, 2013%0a%0a!!! Processing%0a* Casey Reas and Ben Fry, '''Getting Started with Processing''', Published June 2010, O'Reilly Media. 208 pages. Paperback%0a* Hartmut Bohnacker, Benedikt Gross, Julia Laub, and Claudius Lazzeroni, '''Generative Design''' August 2012, Princeton Architectural Press%0a* Jan Vantomme, '''Processing 2: Creative Programming Cookbook''',Published September 2012, PACKT. 350 pages. Paperback and eBook%0a%0a!!! Interacció%0a* Joshua Noble, '''Programming Interactivity''', Published January 2012, O'Reilly.%0a* Shneiderman, B. i Plaisant, C., '''Diseño de interacción de usuario. Estrategias para una interacción persona-computadora efectiva''' Pearson-Addison Wesley, Madrid, 2006%0a* R. Klanten, S. Ehmann, V. Hanschke, '''Touch of code. Interactive installations and experiencies''', 2011, Gestalten%0a* André Knörig, [[http://andreknoerig.de/portfolio/35/bin/Knoerig08_DesignToolsDesign.pdf | '''Design tools design''']], 2008%0a* Jan Barth, Roman Stefan Grasy, Jochen Leinberger, Mark Lukas, Markus Lorenz Schilling. [[http://prototypinginterfaces.com/ | Prototyping Interfaces: Interaktives Skizzieren mit vvvv, Gebundene Ausgabe ]]%0a%0a!!!Generals%0a* Donald A. Norman, [[http://www.loop.la/descargas/disenho/Psicologia_objetos_cotidianos%2520-%2520Donald%2520Norman.pdf | '''Psicologia de los objetos cotidianos''']]%0a* McComb, Gordon '''Electronics for dummies''', Hoboken, N.J. : Wiley, cop. 2005%0a* [[http://fffff.at/TheManual/The_FAT_Manual_Link_Editions_2013.pdf | '''Free Art and Technologic Manual''']]
